In details:Guidatv.uno Acceptance of Conditions These Terms of Service contain the terms and conditions governing the use of the services offered by CoolStreaming.us.
By accepting such conditions during the process of registering to the Site, and using the Site itself, you must explicitly comply with the Site Terms.
The User expressly accepts the additional rules on the page.
Http://www.coolstreaming.us/ .Data Treatment HolderThe Data Controller for the data collected through the Site is CoolStreaming.us, email address Email: privacy@coolstreaming.us Changing Conditions
The terms of service may be modified at any time by an unquestionable judgment of the holders, if they deem it necessary for legal or technical reasons.

Subject to the ordinary lawful remedies provided by law for breach of contract obligations or non-compliance with current regulations, CoolStreaming.us reserves the right to send alerts to the User, suspend fixed-term or indefinite use, interrupting the supply Of all or some of its services, in the case of:

(A) breach of these General Conditions; B) the Site is unable to verify the authenticity of the information provided when registering or using the service; C) the performance of actions that may result in economic damages or legal liability to the Site or other Users; D) security reasons and prevention of unauthorized access to the Site; (E) partial or total cessation of services.
Cookie policyTo make this site work, we sometimes install on your device small data files called "cookies".
Most major sites also do the same.What are cookies?A cookie is a small text file that sites save on your computer or mobile device while you visit them.

Thanks to cookies, the site remembers your actions and preferences (eg login, language, font size, and other display settings) so you do not have to re-enter it when you return to the site or navigate from one page to another.

How and what cookies do we use?NameTypePurpose and description of cookiesCookie WordPressNavigation CookiesCookies have the exclusive logging-in function of allowing users to browse the magazine even in restricted areas.
Cookie VBulletinNavigation CookiesCookies have the function of recognizing logged-in users by enabling web site navigation even in restricted areas.
In addition to this, there are also session cookies for the proper functioning of the Forum.
Performance CookiesNavigation CookiesCookies have the function of saving information on inline style sheets to speed up subsequent user visits and offer faster and cheaper navigation.

Google AnalyticsThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses this kind of web analytics service provided by Google Inc. to have aggregate statistical information useful to evaluate the use of the website and the activities carried out by the visitor.
Google stores the cookie information collected on servers that can be located in the United States.
Google reserves the right to transfer the information collected with its cookie to third parties where this is required by law or where the third party processes information on its behalf.
Google will not associate your IP address with any other data owned by Google in order to obtain a more detailed user profile.
More privacy and / or how to refuse or delete this type of cookie are available at the URL: http://www.google.com/intl/en/analytics/privacyoverview.html .
You can selectively disable Google Analytics by installing the opt-out component provided by Google on your browser.

To disable data collection by Google Analytics, please refer to the following link: https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptoutEmbedded ContentThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us sometimes uses non-constant Youtube videos and other Livestreaming Platforms, social networking content, Facebook, Google+ and, in general, embeddable content on other platforms.
CoolStreaming.us can not control the cookies that these third-party sites supply, and therefore it is advisable to inquire directly at any third party for more control over these cookies.

Below are some useful links to the third-party cookie policy cited:CrazyEggThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us occasionally uses these cookies to optimize the web pages of your site by analyzing user movements anonymously within the site.
For more information on CrazyEgg policies, visit the link https://www.crazyegg.com/privacy .

To disable all CrazyEgg cookies instead, use the following link: https://www.crazyegg.com/opt-outDoubleClickThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us to show banners within the pages uses DoubleClick's third-party service.
The service is used basically and therefore without any kind of behavioral analysis.

For more information about the cookies involved, please use the followinglink http://www.google.com/policies/technologies/ads/ .NewRelicThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us to enhance the site's user experience and enhance performance utilizes a RUM tool called NewRelic.
For information about the cookies in this tool, see the https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/browser/new-relic-browser/page-load-timing-resources/new-relic-cookies link.
Google FontsThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses some parts of the font site from the Google Fonts service.
For information about the cookies involved, please see the link https://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/privacy/CloudflareThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses as a Cloudflare DNS service.
The service provides on-demand security and site security options that, when triggered, may provide cookies for the correct operation.
For information about the cookies in question, see the link https://www.cloudflare.com/security-policyMGIDThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses as a MGD sharing service.
For information about the cookies in question, see the link https://www.mgid.com/privacy-policyTeads.tvThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses as Teads.tv Video Advertising Service.

For information about the cookies in question here is the link http://teads.tv/privacy-policy/ShareThisThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses as sharing service on social networks and related Sharethis.com.
For information about the cookies in question here is the link http://www.sharethis.com/privacy/TradedoublerThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses Tradedoubler.com as an advertising service.

For information about the cookies in question here is the link http://www.tradedoubler.com/en/privacy-policy//Daylimotion Partner ADThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses Daylimotion as an video service.
For information about the cookies in question here is the link https://www.dailymotion.com/legal/privacyOnesignalThird party cookiesCoolStreaming.us uses as push-notification service Onesignal.com.

For information about the cookies involved, please visit https://onesignal.com/privacy_policyHow to control coo kies?You can check and / or verify cookies as you like - to learn more, go to aboutcookies.org .
You can clear cookies already on your computer and set up almost all browsers to block the installation.
If you choose this option, you will need to manually edit some preferences each time you visit the site and some services or certain features may not be available.
